<|channel>thought
<channel|># 詞: 睇怕

1. 佢咁懶，我睇怕佢今次又考唔及格。 (He is so lazy; I'm afraid he'll fail the exam again this time.)
2. 出面落緊大雨，我睇怕陣間會塞車。 (It's raining heavily outside; I'm afraid there will be a traffic jam later.)
3. 佢把口咁毒，我睇怕佢會得罪晒所有同事。 (He is so sharp-tongued; I'm afraid he'll offend all his colleagues.)
4. 呢件衫雖然靚，但係我睇怕唔啱我身。 (This piece of clothing is beautiful, but I'm afraid it won't fit me.)
5. 佢最近成日遲到，我睇怕老闆會鬧佢。 (He has been arriving late lately; I'm afraid the boss will scold him.)
6. 呢個計劃太理想化，我睇怕實際執行到會好困難。 (This plan is too idealistic; I'm afraid it will be very difficult to implement in practice.)
7. 佢咁唔小心，我睇怕佢會整爛個杯。 (He is so careless; I'm afraid he'll break the glass.)
8. 聽日要見家長，我睇怕我老竇會好嬲。 (I have a parent-teacher meeting tomorrow; I'm afraid my dad will be very angry.)
9. 呢間餐廳排隊排得咁長，我睇怕要等成個鐘。 (The queue for this restaurant is so long; I'm afraid we'll have to wait for an hour.)
10. 佢對呢件事完全唔知情，我睇怕佢會好驚。 (He is completely unaware of this matter; I'm afraid he will be very frightened.)

完成10句例句 [end of text]


